    },
    {
        " in which tanks, mechanized infantry and horsed cavalry were mixed. They were also used in the exploitation and pursuit phases of offensives. Red Army mechanized infantry were generally ": null
    },
    {
        "carried on tanks": "Tank Desant"
    },
    {
        " or trucks, with only a few dedicated lend-lease half-track APCs.     The ": null
