    },
    {
        " of a roughly similar composition to a Soviet mechanized corps, which fought in the ": null
    },
    {
        "Italian Campaign": "Italian Campaign"
    },
    {
        ", but it had little scope for mobile operations until near the end of the war.     The ": null
