        " fully tracked tractors. Mark Axworthy, Cornel I. Scafeș, Cristian Crăciunoiu, Third Axis, Fourth Ally: Romanian Armed Forces in the European War, 1941-1945, Arms and Armour, 1995, pp. 87 and 124 The Romanians also produced five prototypes of an ": null
    },
