    },
    {
        "AMX-10P": "Amx-10P"
    },
    {
        ".     The transport and other logistic requirements have led many armies to adopt wheeled APCs when their existing stocks of tracked APCs require replacement. An example is the Canadian Army, which has used the ": null
    },
    {
        "LAV III": "Lav Iii"
    },
    {
